featuredSessions.title: Build What’s Next with Google
featuredSessions.description: ᐳᐅ!DEVFESTYYC is bringing an unprecedented lineup of Google technology experts from around the globe to Calgary. Learn from the Googlers and Google Developer Experts shaping the future of AI, Cloud, Web and Mobile for billions of users worldwide and see how top international and local companies are building with Google.
featuredSessions.label: Watch the 2019 Teaser Video!

howItWas.title: More Festival. More Networking. More Fun!
howItWas.description: Get 2 jam-packed days of keynotes, bootcamps, workshops, labs, demos and networking and enjoy an unparalleled festival experience with parties, pop-ups, music and fun around every corner!
howItWas.label: DevFestYYC 2019 is coming!

info.title: Advance Expertise. Master Technology. Learn More.
info.description: ᐳᐅ!DEVFESTYYC will advance your expertise in Google developer platforms and technologies like Gemini, Android Studio, Chrome, Firebase, AR Core, IDX and many more. Master the tools and techniques required to design, architect, develop, scale, launch, secure, integrate and maintain today’s advanced technology solutions.
info.label: DevFestYYC 2019 is coming!

ticketsBlock.ticketsDetails: Your pass grants you access to all keynotes, technical sessions, hands-on workshops and presentations. You'll also get opportunities to meet and network with speakers and community members. Stay tuned for special pop-up events!

blocks.title: World-Class Developers. Right Here.
blocks.description: ᐳᐅ!DEVFESTYYC is produced by GDGYYC, an all volunteer-led, not-for-profit chapter of Google’s world-wide developer ecosystem of 1 million developers, known as Google Developer Groups (GDG).
blocks.highlight: 100% of the proceeds from ᐳᐅ!DEVFESTYYC go back to the developer community.
blocks.text: Our mission is to help developers, data scientists and technologists utilize Google technology to create, design, code and build for everyone. Since our founding in 2017, we have delivered and supported over 100 developer focused events locally and across North America.
